---
title: Roasted Cod With Mini Roast Potatoes & Tomato and Samphire Salsa
description: We love goodCod With Potatoes & Samphire Salsa and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-cod-45bd5b05-cf870b00.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-cod-5e874257330d4f01e9270c42-7f976f5f.pdf
